short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sync your Disney Photopass Photos to Google Photos

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: MousePhotos makes copying your Disney PhotoPass photos to Google Drive effortless.  Simply install this Chrome extension, connect your Google account, and subscribe, and it will automatically copy your Disney photos to a new Album in Google Photos
